<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-39-0738 </DOCNO><TEXT>In this paper, we investigate the existence and uniqueness of the globalsolutions to the initial boundary value problems of nonlinear wave equationsin an exterior domain. When the space dimension n andgt;= 3, the unique globalsolution of the above problem is obtained for small initial data, evenif the nonlinear term is fully nonlinear and contains the unknown functionitself. (author). 10 refs.</TEXT></DOC>